                            <input type="hidden" value="<%=english.answer5%>">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-4 mb-3">
                            <label for="answer6" class="form-label" style="color: #000;">6. His eyes were .... bad that he couldn't read the number plate of the car in front:</label>
                            <p><b>Answer:</b> <%=english.answer6%></p>
                            <p><b>Correct: </b>so</p>
                            <input type="hidden" value="<%=english.answer6%>">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-4 mb-3">
                            <label for="answer7" class="form-label" style="color: #000;">7. The company need to decide .... and for all what it's position is on this point:</label>
                            <p><b>Answer:</b> <%=english.answer7%></p>
                            <p><b>Correct: </b>once</p>
                            <input type="hidden" value="<%=english.answer7%>">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-4 mb-3">
                            <label for="answer8" class="form-label" style="color: #000;">8. Don't put your cup on the ..... if the table - someone will knock it off:</label>
                            <p><b>Answer:</b> <%=english.answer8%></p>
                            <p><b>Correct: </b>edge</p>
                            <input type="hidden" value="<%=english.answer8%>">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-4 mb-3">
                            <label for="answer9" class="form-label" style="color: #000;">9. I'm sorry. I didn't ..... to disturb you:</label>
                            <p><b>Answer:</b> <%=english.answer9%></p>
                            <p><b>Correct: </b>mean</p>
                            <input type="hidden" value="<%=english.answer9%>">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-4 mb-3">
                            <label for="answer10" class="form-label" style="color: #000;">10. The singer ended the concert ..... her most popular song:</label>
                            <p><b>Answer:</b> <%=english.answer10%></p>
                            <p><b>Correct: </b>with</p>
                            <input type="hidden" value="<%=english.answer1%>">
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-12">
                            <h2>Score: <%=score%></h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <div class="row mb-3">
                    <!--Checar-->
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=<%=english.studentemail%>"class="btn col-2 " style="color: #FFF; background-color: #000;">Accept</a>
                        <a href="/mongodb/deleteUser/<%=english.studentemail%>"class="btn col-2 " style="color: #FFF; background-color: #B5070E;">Delete</a>
                        <a href="/admin/student_information"class="btn btn-secondary col-2 " style="color: #FFF;">Back</a>
                    </div>
                    <%});%>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('template/end')%>